Package: spatialT2
Type: Package
Title: Spatial inference and predictions using the univariate and multivariate Spatial-T model.
Version: 1.0
Date: 2021-05-26
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Isabelle",
           family = "Grenier",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "igrenier@ucsc.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Maintainer: Isabelle Grenier <igrenier@ucsc.edu>
Description: This package implements the non-isotropic spatial model Spatial-T?
    Both the univariate and multivariate versions are available. The package
    allows for the MCMC version as well as the marginal maximization version
    which is faster for large spatial datasets.
